{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775842980330,"sessionID":"ses_28783ada5ffesC6B0aqgZEO6N3","part":{"id":"prt_d787d6ea5001MsEvzz7Z1ZZ85C","messageID":"msg_d787d6224001METBlGn9oRMEyb","sessionID":"ses_28783ada5ffesC6B0aqgZEO6N3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-f03cc9fc56f14e9e8210ea82fd5617e7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 Delta Specification: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 基于生成的 client-go 库，构建 WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架，提供 REST API 用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 自定义资源，并支持健康检查、认证和错误处理。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: HTTP 服务框架基础\n10: \n11: 系统 SHALL 在 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块中构建基于标准库 `net/http` 的 HTTP 服务框架，支持路由注册、中间件链和优雅关闭。\n12: \n13: #### 场景: 创建 HTTP 服务器实例\n14: \n15: **GIVEN** `pkg/workloadmanager` 包已存在  \n16: **WHEN** 初始化 HTTP 服务器  \n17: **THEN** 创建 `Server` 结构体，包含 `*http.Server`、路由注册表、中间件链配置和 shutdown channel\n18: \n19: ```go\n20: type Server struct {\n21:     httpServer   *http.Server\n22:     router       *mux.Router\n23:     middlewares  []Middleware\n24:     client       *clientset.Clientset\n25:     shutdownCh   chan struct{}\n26:     config       *Config\n27: }\n28: \n29: type Middleware func(http.Handler) http.Handler\n30: ```\n31: \n32: #### 场景: 启动和优雅关闭\n33: \n34: **GIVEN** Server 实例已配置  \n35: **WHEN** 调用 `Start()` 和 `Shutdown()` 方法  \n36: **THEN** 服务器监听配置的端口和地址，shutdown 时等待现有请求完成或超时\n37: \n38: ```go\n39: func (s *Server) Start(ctx context.Context) error\n40: func (s *Server) Shutdown(ctx context.Context) error\n41: ```\n42: \n43: ### Requirement: 路由注册和分发\n44: \n45: 系统 SHALL 支持基于 path 和 HTTP 方法的路由注册，使用第三方路由库（如 `gorilla/mux`）实现灵活的路由匹配。\n46: \n47: #### 场景: 注册 AgentRuntime 路由\n48: \n49: **GIVEN** Server 实例已创建  \n50: **WHEN** 注册 AgentRuntime 资源的路由  \n51: **THEN** 为 CRUD 操作创建标准 REST 路由\n52: \n53: ```\n54: GET    /apis/v1/agentruntimes              - List\n55: POST   /apis/v1/agentruntimes              - Create\n56: GET    /apis/v1/agentruntimes/{name}       - Get\n57: PUT    /apis/v1/agentruntimes/{name}       - Update\n58: PATCH  /apis/v1/agentruntimes/{name}       - Patch\n59: DELETE /apis/v1/agentruntimes/{name}       - Delete\n60: ```\n61: \n62: #### 场景: 注册 CodeInterpreter 路由\n63: \n64: **GIVEN** Server 实例已创建  \n65: **WHEN** 注册 CodeInterpreter 资源的路由  \n66: **THEN** 为 CRUD 操作创建标准 REST 路由\n67: \n68: ```\n69: GET    /apis/v1/codeinterpreters           - List\n70: POST   /apis/v1/codeinterpreters           - Create\n71: GET    /apis/v1/codeinterpreters/{name}    - Get\n72: PUT    /apis/v1/codeinterpreters/{name}    - Update\n73: PATCH  /apis/v1/codeinterpreters/{name}    - Patch\n74: DELETE /apis/v1/codeinterpreters/{name}    - Delete\n75: ```\n76: \n77: ### Requirement: 中间件系统\n78: \n79: 系统 SHALL 实现可插拔的中间件系统，支持认证、日志记录、请求追踪、错误恢复和 CORS。\n80: \n81: #### 场景: 认证中间件\n82: \n83: **GIVEN** HTTP 请求进入服务  \n84: **WHEN** 请求到达需要认证的路由  \n85: **THEN** 验证请求头中的认证信息，无效时返回 401 Unauthorized\n86: \n87: ```go\n88: func AuthenticationMiddleware(authProvider AuthProvider) Middleware\n89: ```\n90: \n91: #### 场景: 日志中间件\n92: \n93: **GIVEN** HTTP 请求进入服务  \n94: **WHEN** 请求经过日志中间件  \n95: **THEN** 记录请求方法、路径、状态码、延迟和请求 ID\n96: \n97: ```go\n98: func LoggingMiddleware(logger logr.Logger) Middleware\n99: ```\n100: \n101: #### 场景: 恢复中间件\n102: \n103: **GIVEN** HTTP 请求处理中发生 panic  \n104: **WHEN** panic 被 RecoveryMiddleware 捕获  \n105: **THEN** 返回 500 Internal Server Error 并记录 panic 信息\n106: \n107: ```go\n108: func RecoveryMiddleware(logger logr.Logger) Middleware\n109: ```\n110: \n111: #### 场景: CORS 中间件\n112: \n113: **GIVEN** 浏览器发起跨域请求  \n114: **WHEN** 请求经过 CORS 中间件  \n115: **THEN** 响应包含适当的 CORS 头（Access-Control-Allow-Origin 等）\n116: \n117: ```go\n118: func CORSMiddleware(allowedOrigins []string) Middleware\n119: ```\n120: \n121: ### Requirement: HTTP 处理器（Handlers）\n122: \n123: 系统 SHALL 为每个 CRUD 操作实现处理器函数，使用 client-go 库与 Kubernetes API 交互。\n124: \n125: #### 场景: 创建 AgentRuntime\n126: \n127: **GIVEN** 有效的 AgentRuntime 请求体  \n128: **WHEN** POST /apis/v1/agentruntimes  \n129: **THEN** 验证请求体，调用 client-go Create，返回创建的资源（201 Created）或错误\n130: \n131: ```go\n132: func (h *AgentRuntimeHandler) Create(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n133: ```\n134: \n135: #### 场景: 获取 AgentRuntime\n136: \n137: **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 名称存在  \n138: **WHEN** GET /apis/v1/agentruntimes/{name}  \n139: **THEN** 调用 client-go Get，返回资源（200 OK）或 404 Not Found\n140: \n141: ```go\n142: func (h *AgentRuntimeHandler) Get(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n143: ```\n144: \n145: #### 场景: 列出 AgentRuntime\n146: \n147: **GIVEN** Kubernetes 集群中有多个 AgentRuntime  \n148: **WHEN** GET /apis/v1/agentruntimes  \n149: **THEN** 调用 client-go List，支持 label selector 和 field selector 查询，返回列表（200 OK）\n150: \n151: ```go\n152: func (h *AgentRuntimeHandler) List(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n153: ```\n154: \n155: #### 场景: 更新 AgentRuntime\n156: \n157: **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 名称存在且请求体有效  \n158: **WHEN** PUT /apis/v1/agentruntimes/{name}  \n159: **THEN** 调用 client-go Update，返回更新后的资源（200 OK）或错误\n160: \n161: ```go\n162: func (h *AgentRuntimeHandler) Update(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n163: ```\n164: \n165: #### 场景: 删除 AgentRuntime\n166: \n167: **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 名称存在  \n168: **WHEN** DELETE /apis/v1/agentruntimes/{name}  \n169: **THEN** 调用 client-go Delete，返回 204 No Content 或错误\n170: \n171: ```go\n172: func (h *AgentRuntimeHandler) Delete(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n173: ```\n174: \n175: #### 场景: CodeInterpreter CRUD 操作\n176: \n177: **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter 处理器已注册  \n178: **WHEN** 执行 CodeInterpreter 的 CRUD 操作  \n179: **THEN** 行为与 AgentRuntime 一致，使用 `codeinterpreter` 资源类型\n180: \n181: ### Requirement: 健康检查端点\n182: \n183: 系统 SHALL 提供健康检查端点，用于 K8s liveness 和 readiness probes。\n184: \n185: #### 场景: Liveness probe\n186: \n187: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager Pod 正在运行  \n188: **WHEN** GET /health (liveness)  \n189: **THEN** 返回 200 OK 和健康状态\n190: \n191: ```go\n192: func (s *Server) LivenessProbe(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n193: ```\n194: \n195: #### 场景: Readiness probe\n196: \n197: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 已准备好接收请求  \n198: **WHEN** GET /ready (readiness)  \n199: **THEN** 检查与 Kubernetes API 的连接性，返回 200 OK 或 503\n200: \n201: ```go\n202: func (s *Server) ReadinessProbe(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n203: ```\n204: \n205: ### Requirement: 错误处理和响应\n206: \n207: 系统 SHALL 实现统一的错误处理和 JSON 响应格式。\n208: \n209: #### 场景: 错误响应格式\n210: \n211: **GIVEN** HTTP 处理中发生错误  \n212: **WHEN** 返回错误响应  \n213: **THEN** 使用统一的 JSON 错误格式\n214: \n215: ```json\n216: {\n217:   \"code\": \"RuntimeNotFound\",\n218:   \"message\": \"AgentRuntime 'my-runtime' not found\",\n219:   \"details\": {\n220:     \"name\": \"my-runtime\",\n221:     \"namespace\": \"default\"\n222:   }\n223: }\n224: ```\n225: \n226: #### 场景: Kubernetes API 错误转换\n227: \n228: **GIVEN** client-go 返回 Kubernetes API 错误  \n229: **WHEN** 错误传递到 HTTP 层  \n230: **THEN** 将 Kubernetes 错误转换为适当的 HTTP 状态码和错误消息\n231: \n232: ```go\n233: func K8sErrorToHTTP(err error) (int, *ErrorResponse)\n234: ```\n235: \n236: ### Requirement: 配置管理\n237: \n238: 系统 SHALL 支持从环境变量和配置文件加载配置。\n239: \n240: #### 场景: 加载配置\n241: \n242: **GIVEN** 环境变量和配置文件已设置  \n243: **WHEN** 服务器启动  \n244: **THEN** 从以下来源加载配置并合并：环境变量、配置文件、默认值\n245: \n246: ```go\n247: type Config struct {\n248:     ListenAddr     string\n249:     Port           int\n250:     KubeConfigPath string\n251:     LogLevel       string\n252:     MetricsEnabled bool\n253:     RedisAddr      string\n254:     RedisPassword  string\n255: }\n256: \n257: func LoadConfig() (*Config, error)\n258: ```\n259: \n260: ### Requirement: 指标和追踪\n261: \n262: 系统 SHALL 集成 Prometheus 指标和分布式追踪支持。\n263: \n264: #### 场景: Prometheus 指标\n265: \n266: **GIVEN** HTTP 请求处理中  \n267: **WHEN** 记录指标  \n268: **THEN** 暴露标准 HTTP 指标（请求计数、延迟、活跃连接）和业务指标\n269: \n270: ```\n271: GET /metrics - Prometheus metrics endpoint\n272: ```\n273: \n274: ```go\n275: func MetricsMiddleware(reg prometheus.Registerer) Middleware\n276: ```\n277: \n278: ### Requirement: 请求验证\n279: \n280: 系统 SHALL 在处理器之前验证请求数据。\n281: \n282: #### 场景: 请求体验证\n283: \n284: **GIVEN** HTTP 请求包含 JSON body  \n285: **WHEN** 请求进入处理器  \n286: **THEN** 验证 JSON 格式和必需字段，无效时返回 400 Bad Request\n287: \n288: ```go\n289: func ValidateRequestBody(obj interface{}) error\n290: func ValidationMiddleware(schema validation.Schema) Middleware\n291: ```\n292: \n293: ### Requirement: 客户端注入\n294: \n295: 系统 SHALL 支持依赖注入 client-go 客户端到处理器。\n296: \n297: #### 场景: 注入 Kubernetes 客户端\n298: \n299: **GIVEN** Server 已配置 kubeconfig  \n300: **WHEN** 创建处理器  \n301: **THEN** 将 `*clientset.Clientset` 注入到处理器结构体中\n302: \n303: ```go\n304: type AgentRuntimeHandler struct {\n305:     client  *clientset.Clientset\n306:     logger  logr.Logger\n307:     metrics *Metrics\n308: }\n309: ```\n310: \n311: ### Requirement: Watch 支持\n312: \n313: 系统 SHALL 支持通过 Server-Sent Events (SSE) 或 WebSocket 监听资源变更。\n314: \n315: #### 场景: Watch AgentRuntime 变更\n316: \n317: **GIVEN** 客户端需要监听 AgentRuntime 变更  \n318: **WHEN** GET /apis/v1/agentruntimes?watch=true  \n319: **THEN** 使用 client-go Watch API，通过 SSE 流式传输变更事件\n320: \n321: ```go\n322: func (h *AgentRuntimeHandler) Watch(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n323: ```\n324: \n325: ### Requirement: 文件组织\n326: \n327: 系统 SHALL 按职责分离文件，组织 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块。\n328: \n329: #### 场景: 文件结构清晰分离\n330: \n331: **GIVEN** pkg/workloadmanager 模块需要组织代码  \n332: **WHEN** 创建文件结构  \n333: **THEN** 按职责分离文件：\n334: \n335: ```\n336: pkg/workloadmanager/\n337: ├── server.go              # Server 结构体和启动/关闭逻辑\n338: ├── router.go              # 路由注册和分发\n339: ├── middleware.go          # 中间件实现\n340: ├── handlers.go            # HTTP 处理器接口和基础实现\n341: ├── agentruntime.go        # AgentRuntime 处理器\n342: ├── codeinterpreter.go     # CodeInterpreter 处理器\n343: ├── health.go              # 健康检查端点\n344: ├── response.go            # 响应格式化和错误处理\n345: ├── config.go              # 配置加载和管理\n346: ├── metrics.go             # Prometheus 指标\n347: ├── validation.go          # 请求验证\n348: └── errors.go              # 错误类型和转换\n349: ```\n350: \n351: ## 最终验证\n352: \n353: ### 场景: 端到端集成测试\n354: \n355: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager HTTP 服务已启动并连接到测试 Kubernetes 集群  \n356: **WHEN** 执行完整的 CRUD 操作序列  \n357: **THEN** 所有操作成功返回预期响应，指标正确记录，日志完整输出\n358: \n359: ### 场景: 并发请求处理\n360: \n361: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager HTTP 服务已启动  \n362: **WHEN** 发送多个并发请求  \n363: **THEN** 服务器正确处理所有请求，无竞态条件，响应时间在预期范围内\n364: \n365: ### 场景: 错误场景覆盖\n366: \n367: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager HTTP 服务已启动  \n368: **WHEN** 发送各种错误请求（无效 JSON、不存在的资源、权限错误等）  \n369: **THEN** 服务器返回适当的错误响应，状态码正确，错误消息清晰\n370: \n371: ### 场景: 资源清理\n372: \n373: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 优雅关闭  \n374: **WHEN** 调用 Shutdown()  \n375: **THEN** 所有连接正确关闭，无资源泄漏，进程退出码为 0\n\n(End of file - total 375 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 Delta Specification: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n\n## Purpose\n\n基于生成的 client-go 库，构建 WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架，提供 REST API 用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 自定义资源，并支持健康检查、认证和错误处理。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: HTTP 服务框架基础\n\n系统 SHALL 在 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块中构建基于标准库 `net/http` 的 HTTP 服务框架，支持路由注册、中间件链和优雅关闭。\n\n#### 场景: 创建 HTTP 服务器实例\n\n**GIVEN** `pkg/workloadmanager` 包已存在  \n**WHEN** 初始化 HTTP 服务器  \n**THEN** 创建 `Server` 结构体，包含 `*http.Server`、路由注册表、中间件链配置和 shutdown channel\n\n```go\ntype Server struct {","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775842980313,"end":1775842980328}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775842980333,"sessionID":"ses_28783ada5ffesC6B0aqgZEO6N3","part":{"id":"prt_d787d71bc001dPgRIqTJn4L1LH","messageID":"msg_d787d6224001METBlGn9oRMEyb","sessionID":"ses_28783ada5ffesC6B0aqgZEO6N3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-36446ea395ee4b4fbe6e3733ea622acd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # pkg/workloadmanager — WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework Design\n2: \n3: ## AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework\n4: \n5: **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n6: **Language**: Go  \n7: **Size**: M  \n8: **Purpose**: Provide HTTP API for creating and managing agent runtime sandboxes, implementing session lifecycle management, and integrating with Kubernetes API and Redis storage.\n9: \n10: ## Architecture\n11: \n12: ### Package Structure\n13: \n14: ```\n15: pkg/workloadmanager/\n16: ├── api/\n17: │   ├── agent_runtime.go       # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n18: │   ├── code_interpreter.go    # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n19: │   ├── sandbox.go             # Sandbox creation endpoints\n20: │   ├── middleware.go          # Authentication, logging, recovery\n21: │   └── types.go               # API request/response types\n22: ├── controller/\n23: │   ├── agent_runtime.go       # AgentRuntime controller\n24: │   ├── code_interpreter.go    # CodeInterpreter controller\n25: │   ├── sandbox_manager.go     # Sandbox lifecycle management\n26: │   └── session_lifecycle.go   # Session timeout and cleanup\n27: ├── storage/\n28: │   ├── redis.go               # Redis client wrapper\n29: │   ├── session_store.go       # Session storage interface\n30: │   └── metrics.go             # Storage metrics\n31: ├── auth/\n32: │   ├── jwt.go                 # JWT validation and signing\n33: │   ├── k8s_auth.go            # Kubernetes TokenReview integration\n34: │   └── rbac.go                # RBAC enforcement\n35: ├── config/\n36: │   ├── config.go              # Configuration loading\n37: │   └── validation.go          # Config validation\n38: ├── server/\n39: │   ├── server.go              # HTTP server setup\n40: │   ├── router.go              # Route registration\n41: │   └── health.go              # Health check endpoints\n42: └── client/\n43:     ├── k8s_client.go          # Kubernetes client wrapper\n44:     ├── runtime_client.go      # AgentCube runtime client\n45:     └── sandbox_client.go      # Sandbox API client\n46: ```\n47: \n48: ### Component Interactions\n49: \n50: ```\n51: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n52: │                     WorkloadManager HTTP Server                  │\n53: │                                                                  │\n54: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n55: │  │                    Gin HTTP Layer                        │   │\n56: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │   │\n57: │  │  │           Middleware Chain                         │  │   │\n58: │  │  │  Auth → Logging → Recovery → RBAC → Metrics        │  │   │\n59: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │   │\n60: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │   │\n61: │  │  │              API Handlers                          │  │   │\n62: │  │  │  POST /v1/agent-runtime      → CreateSandbox       │  │   │\n63: │  │  │  POST /v1/code-interpreter   → CreateSandbox       │  │   │\n64: │  │  │  GET  /v1/sessions/:id       → GetSession          │  │   │\n65: │  │  │  DELETE /v1/sessions/:id     → DeleteSession       │  │   │\n66: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │   │\n67: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n68: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n69:          │                     │                     │\n70:          │                     │                     │\n71:          ▼                     ▼                     ▼\n72: ┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐\n73: │  Kubernetes API  │  │     Redis        │  │   Sandbox API    │\n74: │  (client-go)     │  │   (go-redis)     │  │  (agent-sandbox) │\n75: │  - CRDs          │  │  - Session store │  │  - Pod CRUD      │\n76: │  - Pods          │  │  - Activity TTL  │  │  - Secrets       │\n77: │  - Secrets       │  │  - Metadata      │  │  - TokenReview   │\n78: └──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘\n79: ```\n80: \n81: ### Request Flow\n82: \n83: ```\n84: Client Request (Router)\n85:     ↓\n86: [Middleware] Auth Validation\n87:     ↓\n88: [Middleware] RBAC Check\n89:     ↓\n90: [Handler] Parse Request\n91:     ↓\n92: [Controller] Validate Spec\n93:     ↓\n94: [Controller] Create Session Record\n95:     ↓\n96: [Controller] Create Sandbox Pod\n97:     ↓\n98: [Controller] Create JWT Token\n99:     ↓\n100: [Controller] Update Session Metadata\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 1546. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# pkg/workloadmanager — WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework Design\n\n## AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework\n\n**Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: M  \n**Purpose**: Provide HTTP API for creating and managing agent runtime sandboxes, implementing session lifecycle management, and integrating with Kubernetes API and Redis storage.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Package Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── api/\n│   ├── agent_runtime.go       # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n│   ├── code_interpreter.go    # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n│   ├── sandbox.go             # Sandbox creation endpoints\n│   ├── middleware.go          # Authentication, logging, recovery","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md","time":{"start":1775842980316,"end":1775842980330}}}}
