github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` in go.mod\n3. ❌ Missing client-go integration as specified in delta-spec.md:5\n\n**Test Status**:\n- ❌ FAIL: `pkg/workloadmanager/api/response_test.go` - Missing imports (gin, json)\n- ✅ PASS: `pkg/workloadmanager/config/config_test.go`\n\n---\n\n### ❌ Build System - MISSING\n\n**Spec Requirement**:\n- `make gen-client` target\n- `hack/update-codegen.sh` script\n- `k8s.io/code-generator v0.34.1` dependency\n\n**Actual State**:\n- ❌ No Makefile found\n- ❌ No `hack/` directory\n- ❌ No code generation scripts\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n| Component | Status | Details |\n|-----------|--------|---------|\n| client-go library | ❌ FAIL | Not generated, missing from project |\n| API types (pkg/apis) | ✅ PASS | Correctly defined, 65 tests pass |\n| WorkloadManager | ⚠️ PARTIAL | Exists but uses dynamic client |\n| Tests | ❌ FAIL | API response tests fail (missing imports) |\n| Build system | ❌ FAIL | No Makefile or codegen scripts |\n\n### Recommendations\n\n1. **Generate client-go library**: Run `k8s.io/code-generator` to produce `client-go/` directory\n2. **Update WorkloadManager**: Replace dynamic client with typed client from `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n3. **Fix tests**: Add missing imports to `pkg/workloadmanager/api/response_test.go`\n4. **Add build system**: Create Makefile with `gen-client` target and `hack/update-codegen.sh`","time":{"start":1775843019971,"end":1775843019971}}}
